snippet.title: Resist | PlayStation VR2 Launch Trailer | Available now
snippet.description:
Swing, fight, and rise up in a high-speed open-world VR adventure like no other. Step into the shoes of rebel operative Sam Finch and take on a dystopian regime in the definitive version of Resist, fully enhanced for PS VR2.

🕶️ Ultra-smooth 90Hz gameplay
🔆 Enhanced PBR lighting & HDR
🎧 Full headset & Sense controller haptics
🌟 Eye-tracked foveated rendering for peak performance

Explore a massive city, complete story missions and side quests, master fast-paced traversal, and climb the leaderboards as you fight to free Concord from oppression.

📥 Download Resist now on the PlayStation Store
👉 https://store.playstation.com/en-au/concept/10013366

Join the resistance. Defy control. Play Resist today.

#ResistVR #PSVR2 #PlayStationVR2 #VRGaming #LaunchTrailer #NowAvailable #TheBinaryMill #VRActionGame
